    "Most data on your mesh is sent over the primary channel. You can set up secondary channels to create additional messaging groups secured by their own key. [Channel config tips](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/tips/)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die meisten Daten in deinem Mesh werden √ľber den prim√§ren Kanal gesendet. Du kannst sekund√§re Kan√§le einrichten, um zus√§tzliche Nachrichtengruppen zu erstellen, die durch ihren eigenen Schl√ľssel gesichert sind. [Tipps zur Kanalkonfiguration](https://meshtastic.org/docs/configuration/radio/channels/)"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
